column5: Hi all,  Got a bunch of baby walleye and some neat looking little sauger,  The sun went down…….  And then bigger one hit…..23".  An hour well spent!
hey,pull that tape closer to the tail!lol
nice fish    looking forward to chasing a few of those on Erie this summer
Nice Simon.  Nice, drive up,shut up and fish.LOL
a beauty for sure! Those are gonna be some nice filets.
Registering a 23" walleye simon... We all know you'll get a pig... Must wasting your time... Lol
Nice!!... Your gonna have ice till july.. lol
hey,pull that tape closer to the tail!lol Me thinks someone had a few brown pops before measuring lol!, I thought I'd I fix it for you.
